f="https://www.nme.com/news/music/banksys-crude-oil-vettriano-owned-by-blink-182s-mark-hoppus-sells-for-4-3million-3843889">Blink-182的Mark Hoppus拥有的Banksy Post Banksy的“原油（Vettriano）”以430万英镑的价格出售</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出售。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blink-182的Mark Hoppus除了Banksy的“原油（Vettriano）”，在苏富比的伦敦画廊中。 （Tristan的摄影，苏富比的少数图像）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Blink-182s-Mark-Hoppus-poses-by-Banksys-_Crude-Oil-Vettriano_.-Photo-by-Tristan-Fewings_Getty-Images-for-Sothebys-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Banksy">Banksy</a>的“原油（Vettriano）”绘画（曾经由<a href="/artists/Blink-182">Blink 182</a>的<a href="/artists/Mark-Hoppus">Mark Hoppus</a>拥有）在拍卖会上以430万英镑的价格售出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">Blink-182  - “再一次”评论：令人惊讶的触摸聚会</a></strong></li></ul><p>霍普斯（Hoppus）在2011年获得了英国艺术家和激进主义者的稀有且完全手绘的作品。“这幅画对我们来说意义重大，并且是我们生活中如此出色的部分，现在我很高兴能在世界上看到它，并尽可能多地看到。去找&#39;em。 Godspeed，” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182s-mark-hoppus-to-auction-banksys-iconic-crude-oil-vettriano-3839028">音乐家在一份声明中分享。</a></p><p>班克斯（Banksy）的绘画描绘了已故的苏格兰画家杰克·弗特里亚诺（Jack Vettriano）最著名的作品<em>《唱歌的管家》。</em>艺术品的特色是一对夫妇在暴风雨的海滩上跳舞，伴随着他们的管家和女仆，但是，以真正的班克斯（Banksy）形式，在背景中看到了两个穿着黄色危险品西装的数字，可处置油桶。</p><p>当赞美班斯基的一般作品时，霍普斯说：“我喜欢班克斯的艺术。颠覆，幽默，智慧，他妈的你。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGNqJnKRqqn/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,3